title: Have you picked up a Savannah Morning News today?
text:
Photos By Josh Rayburn If you haven’t picked up a copy of today’s Savannah Morning News, you’re missing out.
In addition to stories on how much money your Savannah City Council candidates are raking in from donors and the latest on the Mathew Ajibade death trial, you’ll find ONLY inside:
* 64 pages of savings from Belk
* This week’s best deals from Kroger, Food Lion and Bi-Lo
 * Offers from Badcock & More Home Furniture
* And even more stories about your world, savings from our advertisers, and great finds in our classified ads
